let currentPage = 1
const itemsPerPage = 3
let currentAssociations = []

function initializeMap() {
  const paths = document.querySelectorAll("#map-svg path")
  paths.forEach((path) => {
    path.addEventListener("click", function () {
      const pathId = this.id
      const associations = associationsData[pathId] || associationsData.default
      currentAssociations = associations
      currentPage = 1
      const regionName = getRegionName(pathId)
      displayAssociations(regionName, associations)
      togglePages()
    })
  })
}

function getRegionName(pathId) {
  const regionNames = {
    path01: "Adekar",
    path02: "El Kseur",
    path03: "Béjaia",
    path04: "Tichy",
    path05: "Amizour",
    path06: "Barbacha",
    path07: "Souk El Tenine",
    path08: "Akbou",
    path09: "Seddouk",
    path10: "Tazmalt",
    path11: "Ighil Ali",
    path12: "Darguina",
    path13: "Kherrata",
  }
  return regionNames[pathId] || "Région sélectionnée"
}

function displayAssociations(regionName, associations) {
  const titleElement = document.querySelector("#page-daira h2")
  if (titleElement) {
    titleElement.textContent = `la Daïra de ${regionName}.`
  }
  const associationsContainer = document.getElementById("associations-container")
  if (!associationsContainer) return
  associationsContainer.innerHTML = ""
  const startIndex = (currentPage - 1) * itemsPerPage
  const endIndex = Math.min(startIndex + itemsPerPage, associations.length)
  const displayedAssociations = associations.slice(startIndex, endIndex)
  displayedAssociations.forEach((association, index) => {
    const card = createAssociationCard(association)
    card.style.animationDelay = `${0.1 * (index + 1)}s`
    associationsContainer.appendChild(card)
  })
  updatePaginationControls(associations.length)
}

function createAssociationCard(association) {
  const cardDiv = document.createElement("div")
  cardDiv.className = "col-md-4 mb-4"
  cardDiv.innerHTML = `
        <div class="association-card p-3 h-100">
            <h5 class="text-center fw-bold">Nom de l'association</h5>
            <p class="text-center mb-2">${association.name}</p>
           
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-orange">Adresse maps exacte</h6>
            <p class="mb-1">${association.address}</p>
           
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-orange">Jours de disponibilité</h6>
            <p class="mb-1">${association.availability}</p>
           
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-orange">Types de services</h6>
            <p>${association.serviceType}</p>
        </div>
    `
  return cardDiv
}

function updatePaginationControls(totalItems) {
  const paginationContainer = document.getElementById("pagination-container")
  const prevButton = document.getElementById("prev-page")
  const nextButton = document.getElementById("next-page")
  if (!paginationContainer) return
  const totalPages = Math.ceil(totalItems / itemsPerPage)
  paginationContainer.style.display = totalPages > 1 ? "flex" : "none"
  prevButton.disabled = currentPage === 1
  nextButton.disabled = currentPage === totalPages
  prevButton.onclick = () => {
    if (currentPage > 1) {
      currentPage--
      displayAssociations(getRegionName(getCurrentRegion()), currentAssociations)
    }
  }
  nextButton.onclick = () => {
    if (currentPage < totalPages) {
      currentPage++
      displayAssociations(getRegionName(getCurrentRegion()), currentAssociations)
    }
  }
}

function getCurrentRegion() {
  for (const [regionId, associations] of Object.entries(associationsData)) {
    if (associations === currentAssociations) {
      return regionId
    }
  }
  return "default"
}

function togglePages() {
  const pageMap = document.getElementById("page-map")
  const pageDaira = document.getElementById("page-daira")
  if (pageMap.classList.contains("d-none")) {
    pageDaira.classList.add("fade-out")
    setTimeout(() => {
      pageDaira.classList.add("d-none")
      pageMap.classList.remove("d-none")
      setTimeout(() => {
        pageMap.classList.add("fade-in")
        pageDaira.classList.remove("fade-out")
      }, 50)
    }, 500)
  } else {
    pageMap.classList.add("fade-out")
    setTimeout(() => {
      pageMap.classList.add("d-none")
      pageDaira.classList.remove("d-none")
      setTimeout(() => {
        pageDaira.classList.add("fade-in")
        pageMap.classList.remove("fade-out")
      }, 50)
    }, 500)
  }
}

document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
  initializeMap()
  const returnButton = document.getElementById("return-to-map")
  if (returnButton) {
    returnButton.addEventListener("click", togglePages)
  }
  const paths = document.querySelectorAll("#map-svg path")
  paths.forEach((path) => {
    path.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
      path.style.fill = "rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.2)"
    })
    path.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
      path.style.fill = "white"
    })
  })
})
</script>
